不是
No.

47
00:03:36,630 --> 00:03:39,590
三年前 金画家自杀了
The artist killed himself three years ago.

48
00:03:55,600 --> 00:03:57,810
看来金敏宰的口供是事实
I think Kim Minjae's statement is true.

49
00:04:00,150 --> 00:04:03,070
把尸体送到国科搜 确认一下这是否是金画家的尸体
To see if it really is Artist Kim's body and what the cause of death is,

50
00:04:03,280 --> 00:04:04,400
还有死因是什么
we'll send it to NFS.

51
00:04:04,990 --> 00:04:06,700
-是 罗检察官 -辛苦了
-Yes, ma'am. -Thanks.

52
00:04:11,910 --> 00:04:14,040
金敏宰自首了 甚至还交代了他父亲尸体的位置
His confession and now his body.

53
00:04:15,250 --> 00:04:16,790
事情进展得太顺利了
Things are coming together too easily.

54
