为什么要隐藏金画家自杀的事实
hide the fact that Artist Kim committed suicide

63
00:04:40,110 --> 00:04:41,320
欺骗大家金画家还活着
and say that he was alive?

64
00:04:41,400 --> 00:04:44,530
应该是因为画作吧 毕竟一幅画可以卖几亿韩元
I'm sure it was because of the paintings as one sells for a few hundred million.

65
00:04:44,740 --> 00:04:46,650
他们并不想停止出售金画家的画
They probably didn't want to quit that.

66
00:04:48,070 --> 00:04:50,950
金敏宰是从什么时候 开始代替金画家作画的
Since when did Mr. Kim Minjae start painting for his father?

67
00:04:52,530 --> 00:04:54,540
-从一开始 -什么
-From the beginning. -What?

68
00:04:55,120 --> 00:04:57,370
金敏宰说从一开始就错了
He said it went wrong from the start.

69
00:05:01,880 --> 00:05:03,800
金敏宰和曾是无名画家的父亲
His father, who was an unknown artist,

70
00:05:04,960 --> 00:05:09,050
原本过着穷苦但幸福的生活
and Kim Minjae were poor but lived a happy life.

71
00:05:11,010 --> 00:05:12,510
这是非常具有独创性的画法啊
What a creative drawing technique.

72
00:05:13,260 --> 00:05:16,060
这幅画是你画的吧
This painting is yours, isn't it?

73
00:05:16,270 --> 00:05:17,390
是的
Yes, it is.

74
00:05:19,270 --> 00:05:22,480
他想要维护父亲的颜面 而说了那句谎言
That lie he said to save his father's face

75
00:05:22,810 --> 00:05:24,400
却成了悲剧的开始
became the start of the tragedy.

76
00:05:26,110 --> 00:05:28,610
敏宰 如果太累就别费心画画了
Minjae, if it's too tough, don't force yourself to paint.

77
00:05:29,780 --> 00:05:32,570
如果敏宰不画 你要代替他画吗
If he doesn't do it, will you do it for him?

78
00:05:33,490 --> 00:05:35,620
你能画得像敏宰一样好吗
Can you even paint as well as Minjae?

79
00:05:35,700 --> 00:05:37,250
老婆 对不起
Honey, I'm sorry.

80
00:05:37,580 --> 00:05:39,540
我们别在这里说 还是出去谈吧
Let's not do this here. Let's go elsewhere to talk.

81
00:05:39,830 --> 00:05:41,580
在他们结婚之后 柳熙珠知道了真相
After their marriage, Yoo Heeju found out the truth,

82
00:05:41,710 --> 00:05:43,090
但对她来说 真相并不重要
but it wasn't important to her.

83
00:05:44,170 --> 00:05:46,340
因为比起真相 谎言能创造更多的财富
Because the lie rather than the truth made more money.

84
00:05:46,550 --> 00:05:48,260
敏宰 你父亲…
Minjae, your father…

85
00:05:51,090 --> 00:05:54,220
最终金画家承受不了谎言般的生活
In the end, Artist Kim couldn't stand the lies

86
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:57,430
选择了自杀
and took his own life.

87
00:06:13,240 --> 00:06:14,530
不要啊
No…

88
00:06:15,870 --> 00:06:18,910
他是为了作为无名画家的父亲 才说了那样的话
He said that for the sake of his father who was an unknown artist,

89
00:06:19,500 --> 00:06:20,540
