It's on. Mr. Cheon, your favorite show UI is on.

110
00:07:44,960 --> 00:07:46,000
你不看吗
Aren't you going to watch it?

111
00:07:46,580 --> 00:07:49,960
你先看吧 反正我们都已经知道 节目内容了
Go ahead and start watching. We know the story already, don't we?

112
00:07:50,050 --> 00:07:52,630
在这幢尤为雅致的住宅里…
In this residence that boasts its peacefulness…

113
00:07:52,710 --> 00:07:55,260
但是白实习去哪里了
By the way, where did Ms. Baek go?

114
