Seoul Central District Prosecutor's Office.

533
00:38:28,880 --> 00:38:31,260
现以销毁证据的嫌疑将你紧急逮捕
Mr. Choi Kitae, you're under arrest for destroying evidence.

534
00:38:33,260 --> 00:38:36,390
你是检察官吗 你这个人还挺有意思
You're a prosecutor? You're an interesting guy.

535
00:38:36,470 --> 00:38:39,640
如果你跟我走一趟 会更有意思
If you come with me, it'll become more interesting.

536
00:38:39,730 --> 00:38:40,770
检察官
Listen, prosecutor guy,

537
00:38:41,940 --> 00:38:43,270
你知道我是谁吗
do you know who I am?

538
00:38:44,310 --> 00:38:45,900
嗯 我很清楚你是谁
Yes, I definitely know who you are.

539
00:38:46,400 --> 00:38:48,820
只要我打一通电话 你们就都完了
You guys are all dead with this one phone call.

540
00:38:48,900 --> 00:38:52,490
你可能要请最贵的律师
You'll have to hire the most expensive lawyer.

541
00:39:03,710 --> 00:39:04,710
喂？
Hello.

542
00:39:06,090 --> 00:39:08,590
有什么事 崔基泰社长
What is it, President Choi Kitae?

543
00:39:13,130 --> 00:39:14,680
你为什么给我打电话
Why did you call?

544
00:39:17,260 --> 00:39:19,640
我告诉你要请最贵的律师
I told you to call the most expensive lawyer,

545
00:39:20,230 --> 00:39:21,230
但你却打给了我们部长
but you called my boss.

546
00:39:21,850 --> 00:39:23,190
他一点能力都没有
He has no power.

547
00:39:23,440 --> 00:39:24,810
你这家伙…
You little…

548
00:39:26,650 --> 00:39:28,070
你等着瞧
Let's see.

549
00:39:32,650 --> 00:39:34,280
这里的菜真是…
The food here is--

550
00:39:34,360 --> 00:39:35,320
次长
Sir!

551
00:39:36,660 --> 00:39:38,120
-次长好 -次长好
-Welcome. -Welcome.

552
00:39:39,660 --> 00:39:40,750
唉唷 次长好
Hello.

553
00:39:41,410 --> 00:39:42,330
坐下吧
Have a seat.

554
00:39:46,080 --> 00:39:47,130
都坐下吧
Sit.

555
00:39:55,890 --> 00:39:58,010
我听见有电话铃声的声音
I keep hearing a ringing from here.

556
00:40:00,770 --> 00:40:03,230
喂？你为什么总是打电话
Yes, why do you keep calling?

557
00:40:08,150 --> 00:40:09,520
没有用的
It won't work.

558
00:40:10,980 --> 00:40:11,940
我…
I took…

559
00:40:16,160 --> 00:40:17,820
把他们的手机都拿来了
all of them.

560
00:40:25,080 --> 00:40:26,210
你等着
Bring it on.

561
00:40:29,040 --> 00:40:31,670
崔基泰 你不要再炫耀你的人脉了 赶快跟我走吧
Stop bragging about your connections and come with us, Mr. Choi Kitae.

562
00:40:33,880 --> 00:40:34,920
喂？
Hello.

563
00:40:38,090 --> 00:40:39,430
是我
It's me.

564
00:40:40,010 --> 00:40:41,640
你的一个属下到我这里来了
One of your employees is here.

565
00:40:52,820 --> 00:40:54,440
喂？我是千智勋检察官
Yes, this is Prosecutor Cheon Jihun.

566
00:40:54,530 --> 00:40:57,240
喂 混蛋 你当那是什么地方 竟敢随便去
Hey, you jerk! How dare you go there?

567
00:40:58,110 --> 00:40:59,410
赶紧从那里撤退
Pull out from there right now.

568
00:41:06,660 --> 00:41:08,040
-在这边吗 -对
-This way? -Yes.

569
00:41:08,540 --> 00:41:09,540
智勋
Jihun.

570
00:41:12,050 --> 00:41:15,170
千检察官 外面已经搜查完了
Prosecutor Cheon, we're all done out there.

571
00:41:16,760 --> 00:41:19,220
好好听上级的话 你才能出人头地
You'll go far if you listen to your boss.

572
00:41:22,180 --> 00:41:23,350
他在说什么啊
What is he saying?

573
00:41:25,850 --> 00:41:27,810
次长发了很大的火
The deputy prosecutor general is very mad.

574
00:41:29,150 --> 00:41:30,980
他已经收到风声了？
Has he already caught wind of it?

575
00:41:31,940 --> 00:41:32,980
嗯
Yes.

576
00:41:33,230 --> 00:41:34,480
那我们该怎么办
Then, what happens to us now?

577
00:41:37,240 --> 00:41:38,450
所以说啊
So…

578
00:41:39,280 --> 00:41:41,280
大家都在聚餐 你们来这里干什么
why did you come here when everyone else went for drinks?

579
00:41:41,370 --> 00:41:42,740
平白让自己陷入进退两难的地步
You just got yourselves in trouble.

580
00:41:43,620 --> 00:41:47,370
你们现在走人还不晚 我会帮你们美言几句
It isn't too late to go back. I'll put in a good word for you.

581
00:41:48,670 --> 00:41:49,790
还是说
What do you want?

582
00:41:50,630 --> 00:41:52,630
我跟你们去检察厅坐一会儿
I can drop by the prosecutor's office for a bit,

583
00:41:53,880 --> 00:41:55,210
然后再回家？
and then go home.

584
00:42:11,060 --> 00:42:12,480
我们会没事吗
Do you think we'll be okay?

585
00:42:12,560 --> 00:42:13,650
你指什么
What do you mean?

586
00:42:13,730 --> 00:42:16,650
我们来这里搜查 回去肯定会被训斥
We're going to be chewed out for what we did here.

587
00:42:17,570 --> 00:42:18,400
你不害怕吗
Aren't you afraid?

588
00:42:19,320 --> 00:42:20,490
我害怕
I am afraid,

589
00:42:21,490 --> 00:42:22,490
但反正我都已经干了
but I do it anyway.

590
00:42:26,700 --> 00:42:29,620
不过智勋 我都搜了个遍
By the way, Jihun, I looked everywhere,

591
00:42:29,710 --> 00:42:33,330
可重要的资料似乎都被他销毁了
but I think that guy destroyed all the key documents.

592
00:42:33,630 --> 00:42:34,960
如果我们现在把他带回去
If we take him in at this rate,

593
00:42:35,040 --> 00:42:37,260
就和他说的一样 我们得马上放了他
we'll have to release him immediately as he said.

594
00:42:38,420 --> 00:42:39,420
怎么办
What should we do?

595
00:42:40,220 --> 00:42:41,680
民赫 今天是几号啊
What's the date today, Minhyeok? Hmm.

596
00:42:42,390 --> 00:42:43,430
今天？今天是16号
Today? It's the 16th.

597
00:42:46,890 --> 00:42:48,100
喂？
Hello.

598
00:42:48,180 --> 00:42:49,600
你在哪里
Where are you?

599
00:42:49,680 --> 00:42:53,150
天啊 你时隔一年给我打电话 居然是问我在哪里
Geez, you call me in a year and you ask me where I am?

600
00:42:54,440 --> 00:42:57,980
自从我因为你被赶走 我都在这里待了多长时间了？
Do you know how long I've been here since I got kicked out because of you?

601
00:42:58,900 --> 00:42:59,940
什么
What?

602
00:43:01,740 --> 00:43:04,700
你觉得我还会相信你说的话吗
Do you think I'd believe what you say again?

603
00:43:10,580 --> 00:43:13,210
-走吧 -喂 智勋
-Let's go. -Hey, Jihun.

604
00:43:15,080 --> 00:43:16,380
你让我们就这样回去？
You want us to go back like this?

605
00:43:16,960 --> 00:43:18,800
我觉得你要变得有名一点 民赫
I think you should become famous, Minhyeok.

606
00:43:22,300 --> 00:43:23,590
他在说什么啊
What is he saying?

607
00:43:29,640 --> 00:43:30,810
2017年首尔艺术电影节

608
00:43:50,200 --> 00:43:51,290
帝勋 和我结婚吧
MARRY ME, JEHOON

609
00:43:51,500 --> 00:43:53,000
帝勋哥哥的美貌是范本
JEHOON'S BEAUTY IS THE STANDARD BEAUTY

610
00:44:02,170 --> 00:44:03,510
李帝勋
Mr. Lee Jehoon!

611
00:44:04,340 --> 00:44:07,300
李帝勋 请看这边
Mr. Lee Jehoon, please look over here!

612
00:44:07,510 --> 00:44:08,600
李帝勋
Mr. Lee Jehoon!

613
00:44:09,640 --> 00:44:10,720
请看一下这边
Please look over here.

614
00:44:12,430 --> 00:44:13,730
请看着这里 说几句吧
Look here and say something.

615
00:44:14,770 --> 00:44:17,230
参加如此盛大的活动 我十分紧张
Ah. I'm so nervous to be at such a great event.

616
00:44:17,310 --> 00:44:19,770
希望活动能够圆满成功
I hope that it finishes as a big success.

617
00:44:19,860 --> 00:44:20,780
谢谢
Thank you.

618
00:44:20,860 --> 00:44:22,030
谢谢
Thank you.

619
00:44:25,240 --> 00:44:28,830
真是的 他时隔一年给我打电话 都在胡说什么啊
Darn it. He calls me in a year and what does he have to say now?

620
00:44:29,780 --> 00:44:32,080
又有什么事 为什么老是给我打电话
What do you want? Why do you keep calling me?

621
00:44:35,580 --> 00:44:36,540
喂？
Hello.

622
00:44:44,590 --> 00:44:46,090
我可以让你重新回到社会部
I'll get you back on local news.

623
00:45:05,570 --> 00:45:06,990
大家好
Hello!

624
00:45:08,110 --> 00:45:09,200
真是独家新闻啊
This is a scoop.

625
00:45:13,200 --> 00:45:14,620
他是坏人
He's a bad guy.

626
00:45:19,170 --> 00:45:20,840
看这边
Yes, over here!

627
00:45:24,010 --> 00:45:25,550
JQ建设代表崔基泰 踏上了首尔艺术电影节的红毯
JQ CONSTRUCTION CEO CHOI KITAE ON THE RED CARPET…

628
00:45:25,760 --> 00:45:29,050
富三代和检察官一同站在红毯上
"Third Generation Chaebol and a Prosecutor Stand Together on the Red Carpet."

629
00:45:30,050 --> 00:45:31,760
你这家伙为什么会出现在那里啊
Why would you stand there, you jerk?

630
00:45:31,970 --> 00:45:33,470
你在拍电影吗
Are you filming a movie? Why would a prosecutor go there?

631
00:45:33,560 --> 00:45:34,810
检察官为什么去走红毯啊
Are you filming a movie? Why would a prosecutor go there?

632
00:45:35,220 --> 00:45:36,480
对不起 金部长
I'm sorry, sir.

633
00:45:36,560 --> 00:45:38,900
但我真的不知道
But I really didn't know.

634
00:45:38,980 --> 00:45:42,110
你不知道？你真的不知道吗
You didn't know? Did you really not know?

635
00:45:42,320 --> 00:45:44,690
什么都不知道的家伙 还笑得这么开心吗
How could you be smiling like this if you didn't know? How?

636
00:45:44,980 --> 00:45:46,780
你仔细看的话
If you look carefully,

637
00:45:47,610 --> 00:45:49,740
就会发现我不是在笑
I'm not smiling.

638
00:45:49,820 --> 00:45:51,660
我是还没有完全睡醒
I'm simply not fully awake.

639
00:45:51,740 --> 00:45:53,080
你觉得呢 前辈
What do you think, Yejin?

640
00:45:55,580 --> 00:45:57,290
我最近事情太多了
I've been working a lot lately,

641
00:45:57,580 --> 00:45:59,540
就在车上打了一会儿盹
so I fell asleep in the car briefly and woke up.

642
00:45:59,620 --> 00:46:02,080
结果一下车就发现那里全是记者
When I got out of the car, there were reporters everywhere.

643
00:46:02,170 --> 00:46:04,670
我还以为他们是察觉到了什么 所以都来了
I thought for sure it was because the reporters caught wind of it.

644
00:46:04,880 --> 00:46:07,970
我真的没想到那里在走红毯
I never thought in a million years that it was the red carpet.

645
00:46:09,970 --> 00:46:11,640
你是怎么拿到搜查令的
How did you get the warrant?

646
00:46:12,220 --> 00:46:13,640
聚餐的时候 我去了一趟洗手间
While I was in the restroom at the party, Prosecutor Seo Minhyeok gave me a call.

647
00:46:13,720 --> 00:46:16,390
徐民赫检察官给我打电话
While I was in the restroom at the party, Prosecutor Seo Minhyeok gave me a call.

648
00:46:16,470 --> 00:46:18,890
他说他拿到了搜查令 但自己去有点害怕
He said he got the warrant but was afraid to go alone.

649
00:46:18,980 --> 00:46:19,940
你可真会说啊
That mouth of yours.

650
00:46:21,600 --> 00:46:22,560
你们俩都给我出去
Both of you, get out!

651
00:46:28,900 --> 00:46:30,280
你至少应该跟我说一声啊
You should've given me a heads-up.

652
00:46:30,990 --> 00:46:32,700
你怎么就和民赫擅自去那里了
How could you two do that on your own?

653
00:46:33,490 --> 00:46:34,870
你刚才不是听到了嘛
You just heard.

654
00:46:35,240 --> 00:46:37,370
我也是因为民赫才不得已过去的
I had no choice but to go because of Minhyeok as well.

655
00:46:40,290 --> 00:46:41,290
那我问问他？
Should I ask him?

656
00:46:42,710 --> 00:46:44,000
还是别问了吧
Well, don't ask him.

657
00:46:45,460 --> 00:46:47,710
徐民赫 你怎么样
Seo Minhyeok, how did it go?

658
00:46:50,470 --> 00:46:52,970
多谢前辈关心
Thanks for your concern, Yejin.

659
00:46:53,970 --> 00:46:55,640
我爸都帮我解决好了
Dad took care of everything for me.

660
00:46:55,720 --> 00:46:57,930
我爸以前是次长的直属前辈
He was the direct senior to the deputy prosecutor general.

661
00:46:58,020 --> 00:47:01,350
你父亲啊 我也想见他一面
Your father. I'd like to meet him one day too.

662
00:47:01,810 --> 00:47:02,980
民赫 真羡慕你
You're lucky, Minhyeok.

663
00:47:03,190 --> 00:47:04,520
有什么好的 只会更麻烦
I'm not lucky. It's just tiresome.

664
00:47:05,860 --> 00:47:08,280
对了 智勋 你看报道了吗
By the way, did you see the news, Jihun?

665
00:47:08,860 --> 00:47:09,820
看了
Yes, I did.

666
00:47:09,900 --> 00:47:11,490
按照约定 登在了头版
It was on the front page as promised.

667
00:47:11,740 --> 00:47:13,160
对 但是…
Yes, but…

668
00:47:14,490 --> 00:47:16,530
咱们的照片照得不太好看
we didn't come out so well.

669
00:47:20,000 --> 00:47:21,370
JQ建设崔基泰代表 成为红毯上的热门话题

670
00:47:21,460 --> 00:47:26,130
这个也不算不好看
It didn't… come out badly either.

671
00:47:28,300 --> 00:47:29,510
你看其他报道了吗
Did you see any other articles?

672
00:47:29,590 --> 00:47:31,260
他们应该不会用同一张照片吧
They didn't use the same photo, did they?

673
00:47:31,840 --> 00:47:33,470
不是用同一张照片啊？
Don't they use the same photo?

674
00:47:37,390 --> 00:47:38,180
谢谢
Thank you.

675
00:47:38,720 --> 00:47:39,850
我先走了
I have to go.

676
00:47:42,060 --> 00:47:43,770
你们真是搞笑
You guys are ridiculous.

677
00:47:44,480 --> 00:47:46,150
你现在打算怎么办啊
What are you going to do now?

678
00:47:46,730 --> 00:47:48,610
他们会请水平高超的律师
They will hire an above-average lawyer.

679
00:47:49,610 --> 00:47:52,110
如果我害怕律师 从一开始我就不会这样做
If I was afraid of lawyers, I wouldn't have started to begin with.

680
00:47:53,280 --> 00:47:54,410
告诉他们不用让着我
Tell them to come at me.

681
00:48:14,010 --> 00:48:15,220
喂 检察官
Hey, prosecutor guy.

682
00:48:18,800 --> 00:48:19,850
一会见
See you later.

683
00:48:20,640 --> 00:48:22,560
好 今天就拜托你了
Yes, looking forward to it.

684
00:48:26,150 --> 00:48:27,150
放开我 该死的
Let go. Damn it.

685
00:48:36,110 --> 00:48:39,950
好的 等羁押合法性审查结束 我就过去
Yes, I'll head over as soon as the habeas corpus proceeding finishes.

686
00:48:40,490 --> 00:48:41,580
好的
Okay.

687
00:48:42,870 --> 00:48:44,120
你觉得你能办到吗
Do you think you can do it?

688
00:48:47,500 --> 00:48:50,420
崔基泰闯的祸可不止一两件
This isn't Mr. Choi Kitae's first time getting into trouble.

689
00:48:51,420 --> 00:48:54,050
我读那些文件的时候 不知道有多么生气
I got so mad reading the documents.

690
00:48:55,170 --> 00:48:57,840
就应该把他那样的家伙抓起来
Shouldn't a jerk like him be sent to prison

691
00:48:57,930 --> 00:48:59,760
让他赎罪 不是吗
and made to pay for his crimes?

692
00:49:00,890 --> 00:49:04,560
对 当然了 但这里是男卫生间
Yes, you're right. But this is the men's room.

693
00:49:05,940 --> 00:49:08,770
这次他肯定也会花大价钱 请律师帮他脱身
He'll get an expensive lawyer this time and try to get away with it again.

694
00:49:08,850 --> 00:49:09,730
你有信心吗
Can you handle it?

695
00:49:10,190 --> 00:49:12,020
嗯 我有信心 但你是哪位
Yes, I am confident. But who are you?

696
00:49:15,240 --> 00:49:17,530
听说你的调查能力很强
You were known for your investigative abilities.

697
00:49:19,620 --> 00:49:22,870
拜托你了 千智勋检察官
I'm counting on you, Prosecutor Cheon Jihun.

698
00:49:44,220 --> 00:49:46,140
-喂 智勋 -怎么了
-Hey, Jihun. -Yeah?

699
00:49:46,850 --> 00:49:48,850
那家伙有恃无恐啊
That guy must have something up his sleeve.

700
00:49:49,310 --> 00:49:50,150
他在笑
He's smiling.

701
00:50:05,290 --> 00:50:07,750
检察官席
PROSECUTION TABLE

702
00:50:18,720 --> 00:50:20,840
喂 是白法律事务所 我们怎么办
It's Mr. Baek's firm. What do we do?

703
00:50:22,430 --> 00:50:24,220
如果是白法律事务所 那应该花了不少钱
If it's Law Firm Baek, it must've cost a fortune.

704
00:50:25,560 --> 00:50:26,640
你受苦了
Hang in there.

705
00:50:28,390 --> 00:50:31,650
你稍等一下 马上就会有好消息
If you remain patient, we'll bring you some good news.

706
00:50:31,730 --> 00:50:32,940
拜托你了
I'm counting on you.

707
00:50:34,110 --> 00:50:36,030
我们又得和老头们较量一番了
I guess we have to go another round with the old men.

708
00:50:47,160 --> 00:50:49,160
辩护人席
DEFENSE COUNSEL TABLE

709
00:51:02,930 --> 00:51:04,720
原来她是对方的律师啊
She was their lawyer.

710
00:51:05,680 --> 00:51:07,060
什么 谁
What? Who?

711
00:51:08,220 --> 00:51:09,140
没事
Hmm. Nothing.

712
00:51:15,440 --> 00:51:17,570
嫌疑人没有毁灭证据和逃跑之虑
The defendant poses no risk of destroying evidence or fleeing,

713
00:51:17,900 --> 00:51:19,070
并且有准确的居住地址
and his residence is clear.

714
00:51:19,150 --> 00:51:22,700
检方在进行扣押搜查时 已经拿到了大部分相关证据
The prosecution has secured all the evidence during their search,

715
00:51:22,860 --> 00:51:25,120
所以我们认为检方在调查期间
so there is no need for the prosecution to know his whereabouts

716
00:51:25,370 --> 00:51:26,740
没有必要拘留嫌疑人
during their investigation.

717
00:51:27,410 --> 00:51:29,080
另外倘若检方传唤嫌疑人进行调查
Also, when the prosecution requests an investigation,

718
00:51:29,580 --> 00:51:33,370
嫌疑人一定会到检察厅诚实协助调查
the defendant will appear and cooperate with the investigation.

719
00:51:35,040 --> 00:51:36,880
检方 请进行陈述
Prosecution, you may proceed.

720
00:51:37,340 --> 00:51:38,300
是
Yes.

721
00:51:38,670 --> 00:51:40,760
嫌疑人在检方执行扣押搜查的过程中
The defendant was arrested

722
00:51:40,840 --> 00:51:43,840
因为涉嫌毁灭证据被现场逮捕
for trying to destroy evidence during our search

723
00:51:44,550 --> 00:51:48,060
我方怀疑嫌疑人会销毁其他证据 并收买相关人员
and we suspect that there will be additional attempts to destroy evidence,

724
00:51:48,140 --> 00:51:50,980
所以我方认为 需要对其进行拘留调查 审判长
so we think that he must be detained during the investigation, Your Honor.

725
00:52:06,870 --> 00:52:09,700
拘留？当然不能拘留
Detained? Of course, not. I was indicted without detainment.

726
00:52:10,040 --> 00:52:12,750
我现在就过去 你马上出来
Hey, I'm on my way. Come out right now.

727
00:52:20,840 --> 00:52:21,960
李律师
Excuse me.

728
00:52:26,090 --> 00:52:27,470
你在干什么啊
What are you doing right now?

729
00:52:28,140 --> 00:52:29,850
你在耍我吗
Were you playing with me?

730
00:52:29,930 --> 00:52:33,310
我们去喝杯咖啡吧 我请客
Do you want to get some coffee? It's my treat.

731
00:52:49,530 --> 00:52:51,450
咖啡厅咖啡
CAFE COFFEE

732
00:52:52,240 --> 00:52:53,540
加奶的咖啡可以吗
Are you okay with milk coffee?

733
00:52:57,330 --> 00:52:58,830
你不喝自动贩卖机里的咖啡吗
Don't you drink vending machine coffee?

734
00:52:59,750 --> 00:53:01,250
我可以尝一下
I'll give it a try.

735
00:53:02,590 --> 00:53:04,170
你该不会没有喝过这种咖啡吧
You're saying...

736
00:53:04,260 --> 00:53:06,130
你该不会没有喝过这种咖啡吧
...you've never tried it, are you?

737
00:53:10,050 --> 00:53:12,850
天啊 那你肯定会被吓一跳
Gosh. You're in for a surprise.

738
00:53:42,170 --> 00:53:43,300
怎么样
How is it?

739
00:53:44,760 --> 00:53:46,220
还好 甜甜的
Well, it's sweet.

740
00:53:47,420 --> 00:53:49,890
是吧 能让心情变好一点吧
Isn't it? Doesn't it make you feel better?

741
00:53:51,470 --> 00:53:53,470
以后你会经常想喝它的
I'll be seeing you often from now on.

742
00:53:56,310 --> 00:53:59,560
我刚才说的话是发自内心的
I meant… what I said earlier.

743
00:54:01,980 --> 00:54:04,780
犯了罪的人就应该受到应有的惩罚
The person who committed a crime must be punished accordingly.

744
00:54:04,860 --> 00:54:06,110
这就是我的想法
That's what I think.

745
00:54:07,240 --> 00:54:10,240
但不幸的是我是一名律师
Unfortunately, I work as a lawyer.

746
00:54:12,780 --> 00:54:14,950
你应该费了不少劲才抓住他
I'm sure It must've been hard to arrest him.

747
00:54:15,410 --> 00:54:16,250
对不起
I'm sorry.

748
00:54:21,830 --> 00:54:24,420
你有什么好抱歉的 庭审都还没有开始
Why are you sorry? The trial hasn't even started yet.

749
00:54:25,800 --> 00:54:28,380
就像你说的 犯了罪的人
As you said, a jerk that has committed a crime

750
00:54:29,630 --> 00:54:31,590
就应该受到应有的惩罚
must be punished accordingly.

751
00:54:34,180 --> 00:54:35,260
你有信心做到吗
Are you confident about it?

752
00:54:37,930 --> 00:54:39,850
对 我有信心
Yes, I am.

753
00:54:42,770 --> 00:54:46,400
庭审中败诉的人请客喝酒怎么样 千智勋检察官
Shall we say that whoever loses has to buy the other person a drink, Mr. Cheon?

754
00:54:48,610 --> 00:54:51,450
但是我从来没有 在打赌请客喝酒时败诉过
But I've never lost a bet over a drink.

755
00:54:53,820 --> 00:54:56,200
那这次打赌和官司 你就都输一次吧
I guess you'll lose that bet and the trial this time.

756
00:54:58,410 --> 00:54:59,580
那我就等着瞧了
I look forward to it.

757
00:55:08,590 --> 00:55:13,010
你一定要赢下这场官司 拜托你了
Please win this trial. I'm counting on you.

758
00:55:19,680 --> 00:55:22,390
我作为律师也会全力以赴
As an attorney, I'll do my best as well.

759
00:55:24,190 --> 00:55:28,730
好 我之后会考虑要不要喝这杯酒
Yes, I'll decide later on whether I want that drink or not,

760
00:55:29,940 --> 00:55:31,780
但一定会是你来请客
but you're gonna have to buy that drink.

761
00:56:22,410 --> 00:56:25,210
《平价正义》
ONE DOLLAR LAWYER

762
00:57:07,500 --> 00:57:09,290
闯祸的检察官是谁
Who's the prosecutor that caused the trouble?

763
00:57:09,380 --> 00:57:10,500
是千智勋检察官
It's Prosecutor Cheon Jihun.

764
00:57:10,590 --> 00:57:12,920
他太我行我素 连检方那边都放弃他了
He's so stubborn that even the prosecution gave up on him.

765
00:57:13,010 --> 00:57:14,550
他写好了遗书 然后就消失了
He wrote a will and disappeared.

766
00:57:14,630 --> 00:57:15,760
他肯定死在某个地方了
He must've died somewhere!

767
00:57:15,840 --> 00:57:17,510
听起来像是你盼着他死
It sounds like that's what you want.

768
00:57:17,590 --> 00:57:18,840
你这家伙疯了吗
Have you lost your mind?

769
00:57:18,930 --> 00:57:20,430
你为什么让他去死
Why did you tell him to die?

770
00:57:21,260 --> 00:57:22,680
你不是检察官 是作家啊
You aren't a prosecutor. You're a novelist.

771
00:57:22,760 --> 00:57:23,930
-代表 -你有证据吗
-Sir. -Do you have proof?

772
00:57:24,020 --> 00:57:27,230
犯了罪就要受到应有的惩罚 这才是正义
If one has committed a crime, they must be punished accordingly. That's justice.

773
00:57:27,310 --> 00:57:28,940
千检察官 你不谈恋爱吗
Don't you ever go on a date?

774
00:57:29,940 --> 00:57:33,440
我一定会查到秘密资金的流向
I'm going to find out where he siphoned that slush fund.

775
00:57:33,530 --> 00:57:35,110
车牌号是多少
What's the license plate number?

776
00:57:35,190 --> 00:57:37,280
-是N3866 -天啊
-It's N 3866. -Unbelievable.

777
00:57:37,360 --> 00:57:39,410
-是谁 -他现在很忙
-Who is it? -He's been very busy lately.

778
00:57:39,490 --> 00:57:42,740
智勋 不管你做出什么样的选择 我都会站在你这边
Jihun, no matter what choice you make, I'm on your side,

779
00:57:42,830 --> 00:57:43,910
但你可以止步于此
but you can stop here.

780
00:57:44,240 --> 00:57:44,910
-快进来 -你不能调查你的父亲
Welcome.

781
00:57:45,000 --> 00:57:46,370
-快进来 -你不能调查你的父亲
You can't investigate your own father.